properties.text:
PIERCE SHOT

Your arrows PIERCE, allowing you to hit multiple enemies with the same arrow.

[color=#a5a1b4]PIERCE SHOT[/color]

Your arrows [color=#a5a1b4]PIERCE[/color], allowing you to hit multiple enemies with the same arrow.

MULTISHOT

Shoot three arrows in a cone in front of you at the same time.

[color=#a5a1b4]MULTISHOT[/color]

Shoot three arrows in a cone in front of you at the same time.

FIRE ARROWS

Attacks BURN enemies, causing them to take damage over time.

[color=#FF0000]FIRE ARROWS[/color]

Attacks [color=#FF0000]BURN[/color] enemies, causing them to take damage over time.

ELECTRIC ARROWS

Attacks SHOCK enemies, causing damage to spread to nearby enemies.

[color=#f2e600]ELECTRIC ARROWS[/color]

Attacks [color=#f2e600]SHOCK[/color] enemies, causing damage to spread to nearby enemies.

FROST ARROWS

Attacks EMBRITTLE enemies, causing them to take extra arrow damage.

[color=#00f1f2]FROST ARROWS[/color]

Attacks [color=#00f1f2]EMBRITTLE[/color] enemies, causing them to take extra arrow damage.

CHARGED SHOT

Hold the RIGHT MOUSE BUTTON to CHARGE and EMPOWER your arrows, allowing them to ricochet and inflict increased damage upon release.

[color=#a5a1b4]CHARGED SHOT[/color]

Hold the RIGHT MOUSE BUTTON to [color=#a5a1b4]CHARGE[/color] and [color=#a5a1b4]EMPOWER[/color] your arrows, allowing them to ricochet and inflict increased damage upon release.
